    <summary>Indicates the way <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.Brush" />-valued dependency properties are sampled in a custom shader effect.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 Set the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Effects.SamplingMode> when you define a dependency property for a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Effects.ShaderEffect>.  
  
 The rendering system automatically selects the appropriate sampling mode, depending on whether hardware or software rendering is enabled, whether the destination texture is rotated, and other factors.  
  
 ]]></format>
